#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SI.rst:3
#: ce598d1352bf4c4fb70cbec2407952bc
msgid ""
"The SI Model [1]_ assumes that infection spreads only through links between "
"neighboring nodes in a graph :math:`G=(V,E)`. Each node is in one of two "
"states: :math:`S` (susceptible) or :math:`I` (infected). A susceptible node "
":math:`i` becomes infected by its infected neighbors :math:`j \\in N(i)` "
"with rate :math:`\\beta`:"
msgstr ""
"SI模型 [1] 假设感染只通过相邻的节点之间的联系在图:math:`G=(V,E)'中传播. "
"每个节点位于两个州中之一:`S'(可接受)或`I'(感染)。 一个易受感染的节点:math:`i ' 被感染的邻居感染 :math:`j\\in "
"N(i)' 比率:math:Q`\\beta':"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SI.rst:7
#: 1a49ff3e77b64aa9916b2c3cbe4bb38a
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"\\frac{dS_i}{dt} &= -\\beta \\sum_{j\\in N(i)} S_i I_j, \\\\\n"
"\\frac{dI_i}{dt} &= \\beta \\sum_{j\\in N(i)} S_i I_j .\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""
"开始{对齐}\n"
"\\ frac{ dS i}{dt}\\\\\\\\\\ beta\\ sum\\j\\ in N(i)}S i I j,\\\\\\\\\n"
"\\ frac{ dI i}{dt}\\\\ beta\\ sum {j\\in N(i)}S i I j.\n"
"结束{对齐}"

