#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SI.rst:59
#: 3cbd64797096492cb8426b3e86412b9b
msgid ""
"Node states are represented by a Boolean indicator vector :math:`h \\in "
"\\{0,1\\}^N`, where :math:`h_i=1` denotes ``infected`` and :math:`h_i=0` "
"denotes ``susceptible``. The update of the system at step :math:`k` is "
"decomposed into three stages:"
msgstr ""
"节点状态用布尔指标矢量表示:math:`h\\ in \\{0,1\\}^N',其中:math:`h i=1'表示‘感染',math:`h "
"i=0'表示‘可接受'。 系统分三个阶段更新:"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SI.rst:63
#: 9d2567cebd3745418f2f156809bc2ca8
msgid ""
"Each infected neighbor :math:`j` of node :math:`i` transmits a log-"
"probability contribution"
msgstr "每个受感染的邻居:math:节点的`j':math:`i ' 传递日志概率贡献"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SI.rst:65
#: c5db6382173f42ba968c60481ef4fc72
msgid "m_{ji}^{(k)} = h_j^{(k-1)} \\cdot \\log(1-\\beta)"
msgstr "m {ji}^{(k)}=h j^{(k-1)}\\cdot\\log(1-\\β)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SI.rst:69
#: a614c740a11d49548a5d0fdbe11d0118
msgid ""
"Node :math:`i` collects contributions from all neighbors :math:`N(i)` to "
"compute its infection probability"
msgstr "节点: \" i \" 收集所有邻居的贡献: \" N(i) \" 计算感染概率"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SI.rst:71
#: d45b3e74eeee4443b6ab555b0283a239
msgid "m_i^{(k)} = 1 - \\exp\\!\\left( \\sum_{j \\in N(i)} m_{ji}^{(k)} \\right)"
msgstr "m i^{(k)}=1 -\\exp\\!\\左(\\sum {j\\in N(i)} m {ji}^{(k)}\\右)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SI.rst:75
#: 29e70f79ecb14cdc8556a6a97a9f870e
msgid ""
"The indicator variable is updated with independent uniform random variables "
":math:`U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}} \\sim \\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)`:"
msgstr ""
"指标变量由独立的统一随机变量更新 : math : `U i ^{\\mathrm{inf}}}\\sim\\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)'"
" :"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/SI.rst:77
#: 8b072722fdcc412f9a80e99e1e16f619
msgid ""
"h_i^{(k)} =\n"
"\\begin{cases}\n"
"   1, & \\text{if } h_i^{(k-1)}=0 \\land (U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}} < m_i^{(k)}), \\\\[4pt]\n"
"   h_i^{(k-1)}, & \\text{otherwise}.\n"
"\\end{cases}"
msgstr ""
"h i^{(k)}=\n"
"开始{ cases}\n"
"1, &\\ text{if} h i^{(k-1)}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\}\n"
"h i^{(k-1)}, &\\ text{另类}.\n"
"结束{ cases}"

